SELECT 
    c.CustomerID, 
    c.CompanyName, 
    SUM(od.UnitPrice * od.Quantity) AS Total,
    CASE 
        WHEN SUM(od.UnitPrice * od.Quantity) < 1000 THEN 'Low'
        WHEN SUM(od.UnitPrice * od.Quantity) BETWEEN 1000 AND 5000 THEN 'Medium'
        ELSE 'High'
    END AS Group
FROM 
    orders o
JOIN 
    order_details od ON o.OrderID = od.OrderID
JOIN 
    customers c ON o.CustomerID = c.CustomerID
WHERE 
    o.OrderDate LIKE '1998%'
GROUP BY 
    c.CustomerID, c.CompanyName
ORDER BY 
    Total DESC
""

""
SELECT 
    p.category_id,
    c.category_name,
    SUM(oi.quantity) AS total_quantity_sold,
    SUM(oi.quantity * oi.list_price * (1 - oi.discount)) AS total_sales_revenue
FROM 
    order_items oi
JOIN 
    orders o ON oi.order_id = o.order_id
JOIN 
    products p ON oi.product_id = p.product_id
JOIN 
    categories c ON p.category_id = c.category_id
WHERE 
    o.order_date BETWEEN '2016-01-01' AND '2018-12-31'
GROUP BY 
    p.category_id, c.category_name
ORDER BY 
    p.category_id
""

""
SELECT 
    p.category_id,
    c.category_name,
    SUM(oi.quantity) AS total_quantity_sold,
    SUM(oi.quantity * oi.list_price * (1 - oi.discount)) AS total_sales_revenue
FROM 
    order_items oi
JOIN 
    orders o ON oi.order_id = o.order_id
JOIN 
    products p ON oi.product_id = p.product_id
JOIN

WHERE

GROUP BY

""

""
SELECT 
    SUM(oi.quantity) AS total_quantity,
    SUM(oi.quantity * oi.list_price * (1 - oi.discount)) AS total_price,
    c.category_name
FROM 
    order_items oi
JOIN 
    orders o ON oi.order_id = o.order_id
JOIN 
    products p ON oi.product_id = p.product_id
JOIN 
    categories c ON p.category_id = c.category_id
WHERE 
    o.order_date BETWEEN '2016-01-01' AND '2018-12-31'
GROUP BY 
    c.category_name
ORDER BY 
    c.category_name
""

""
WITH all_categories AS (
    SELECT category_name FROM categories
)
SELECT 
    COALESCE(SUM(oi.quantity), 0) AS total_quantity,
    COALESCE(SUM(oi.quantity * oi.list_price * (1 - oi.discount)), 0) AS total_price,
    ac.category_name
FROM 
    all_categories ac
LEFT JOIN 
    products p ON ac.category_name = (SELECT category_name FROM categories WHERE category_id = p.category_id)
LEFT JOIN 
    order_items oi ON p.product_id = oi.product_id
LEFT JOIN 
    orders o ON oi.order_id = o.order_id
WHERE 
    o.order_date BETWEEN '2016-01-01' AND '2018-12-31' OR o.order_date IS NULL
GROUP BY 
    ac.category_name
ORDER BY 
    ac.category_name
""

""
WITH BattingStats AS (
    SELECT
        p.Player_Id,
        p.Player_Name,
        COUNT(pm.Match_Id) AS Matches_Played,
        SUM(bs.Runs_Scored) AS Total_Runs,
        SUM(CASE WHEN bs.Runs_Scored = 0 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) AS Ducks,
        SUM(bs.Ball_Id) AS Balls_Faced
    FROM
        Player p
    JOIN
        Player_Match pm ON p.Player_Id = pm.Player_Id
    JOIN
        Batsman_Scored bs ON pm.Match_Id = bs.Match_Id AND p.Player_Id = bs.Player_Id
    GROUP BY
        p.Player_Id, p.Player_Name
)
SELECT
    Player_Id,
    Player_Name,
    Matches_Played,
    Total_Runs,
    Balls_Faced,
    CAST(Total_Runs AS REAL) / Matches_Played AS Batting_Average,
    (CAST(Total_Runs AS REAL) / Balls_Faced) * 100 AS Strike_Rate
FROM
    BattingStats
WHERE
    Matches_Played >= 50
ORDER BY
    Batting_Average DESC,
    Strike_Rate DESC
""

WITH overdue_rentals AS (
    SELECT r.customer_id, COUNT(*) AS overdue_count
    FROM rental r
    WHERE r.return_date IS NULL OR r.return_date > DATE(r.rental_date, '+3 days')
    GROUP BY r.customer_id
),
total_rentals AS (
    SELECT r.customer_id, COUNT(*) AS total_count
    FROM rental r
    GROUP BY r.customer_id
)
SELECT c.first_name, c.last_name, c.email, 
       (CAST(o.overdue_count AS REAL) / t.total_count) * 100 AS overdue_percentage
FROM customer c
JOIN overdue_rentals o ON c.customer_id = o.customer_id
JOIN total_rentals t ON c.customer_id = t.customer_id
ORDER BY overdue_percentage DESC;
""

""
WITH BowlerPerformance AS (
    SELECT
        p.Player_Name,
        p.Country_Name,
        p.Bowling_skill,
        m.Match_Id,
        COUNT(wt.Player_Out) AS Wickets,
        SUM(pm.Runs_Conceded) AS Runs_Conceded
    FROM
        Player p
    JOIN
        Player_Match pm ON p.Player_Id = pm.Player_Id
    JOIN
        Match m ON pm.Match_Id = m.Match_Id
    LEFT JOIN
        Wicket_Taken wt ON m.Match_Id = wt.Match_Id AND pm.Player_Id = wt.Player_Out
    WHERE
        pm.Role_Id = 2  -- Assuming 2 is the role ID for bowlers
    GROUP BY
        p.Player_Id, m.Match_Id
)
SELECT
    Player_Name,
    Country_Name,
    Bowling_skill,
    Wickets,
    Runs_Conceded
FROM
    BowlerPerformance
ORDER BY
    Wickets DESC;
""
